I am a human-centered researcher + designer, thoughtful creative, and writer. Long before I waded into the techscape, I worked as a medical sciences student and laboratory research specialist. 

I have a strong interest in applying human centered research, design and creative strategy towards social innovation and impact, global healthcare, women's rights and education.

Give me your seemingly messiest galaxy of stars and I'll point out the constellations, give me your forests and I will show you the trees, give me chaotic problems and I can find order. 
(and I love doing it!)
